// mockHotelData.js
export const mockHotels = [
  {
    id: 1,
    name: "DoubleTree Hotel",
    distance: "1.2",
    rating: 4.5,
    reviews: 128,
    amenities: ["WiFi", "Pool", "Gym"],
    price: 100, // USD
    images: 3, // Number of images available
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    name: "Marina Bay Sands",
    distance: "3.5",
    rating: 4.8,
    reviews: 452,
    amenities: ["WiFi", "Spa", "Restaurant"],
    price: 350,
    images: 5,
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    name: "The Ritz-Carlton",
    distance: "2.0",
    rating: 4.7,
    reviews: 389,
    amenities: ["WiFi", "Spa", "Gym", "Fine Dining"],
    price: 280,
    images: 4,
  },
  {
    id: 4,
    name: "Hilton Garden Inn",
    distance: "4.1",
    rating: 4.3,
    reviews: 215,
    amenities: ["WiFi", "Gym", "Free Breakfast"],
    price: 120,
    images: 3,
  },
  {
    id: 5,
    name: "Shangri-La Hotel",
    distance: "5.2",
    rating: 4.9,
    reviews: 512,
    amenities: ["WiFi", "Pool", "Spa", "Luxury Suites"],
    price: 400,
    images: 6,
  },
];
